# SAIL Starter Kit - Windsurf Rules

## Project Context

Fullstack platform template with app generation capabilities.

Stack:
- Backend: FastAPI + Pydantic v2 + MongoDB (Motor async)
- Frontend: React 19 + TypeScript + Vite + TailwindCSS v4
- State: Zustand + React Query
- Auth: JWT + bcrypt

## First Time Setup (IMPORTANT)

If this is a fresh clone or the user asks to "start the project":

```bash
./init-project.sh      # Interactive setup - configures app name, colors, .env
docker compose up --build
```

The init script will:
1. Ask for app name, slug, primary color, description
2. Generate system.config.json with your settings
3. Create .env from template with secure defaults
4. Update Docker service names

**DO NOT** just copy .env.example and run docker compose - always use ./init-project.sh first.

After init, access the app at:
- Frontend: http://localhost:3100
- API Docs: http://localhost:3100/api/docs

## Strict Rules

### Forbidden Actions
- NO new frameworks or libraries without approval
- NO modifications to docker-compose.yml without asking
- NO bypassing authentication or RBAC checks
- NO inline CSS - use Tailwind utilities only
- NO raw HTML elements - use design system components
- NO hardcoded colors - use CSS variables
- NO manual file creation in modules/ or pages/generated/

### Required Patterns

**Backend:**
- All DB operations must be async/await
- All functions must have type hints
- All inputs validated with Pydantic
- Use Depends() for dependency injection

**Frontend:**
- Use components from `components/ui/` only
- Use `var(--color-name)` for all colors
- Interfaces for all props
- Functional components with hooks

## Design System Components

Location: `frontend/src/components/ui/`

| Use This | Not This |
|----------|----------|
| `<Button>` | `<button>` |
| `<Input>` | `<input>` |
| `<Select>` | `<select>` |
| `<Card>` | `<div className="border...">` |
| `<Modal>` | Custom modal divs |

## File Structure

```
backend/app/modules/<name>/
├── __init__.py
├── router.py      # FastAPI endpoints
├── schemas.py     # Pydantic models
└── service.py     # Business logic

frontend/src/pages/<Name>.tsx
frontend/src/components/ui/<Component>.tsx
```

## Configuration

- App config: `system.config.json`
- Design tokens: `frontend/src/design-system/design-tokens.css`
- Environment: `.env` (copy from `.env.example`)

## Commands

```bash
./generate-app.sh      # Generate new app module
./verify-project.sh    # Verify project compliance
docker compose up -d   # Start services
```

## Email Providers

Set `EMAIL_PROVIDER` in .env:
- `console` - Development (logs only)
- `smtp` - SMTP server (Gmail, Outlook, etc.)
- `resend` - Resend API

## Protected Files

Review before modifying:
- `backend/app/core/*`
- `backend/app/auth/*`
- `frontend/src/components/ui/*`
- `system.config.json`
